<doc id="176112" wikidata="Q914102" url="?curid=176112" title="Juprelle">
<text>Juprelle (; ) is a municipality of Wallonia located in the province of Liège, Belgium.

On 1 January 2006 Juprelle had a total resident population of 8,405. The total area is 35.36 km2 which gives a population density of 238 inhabitants per km2.

The municipality consists of the following districts: Fexhe-Slins, Juprelle, Lantin, Paifve, Slins, Villers-Saint-Siméon, Voroux-lez-Liers, and Wihogne.

