<text>Olne (; ) is a municipality of Wallonia located in the province of Liège, Belgium.

On January 1, 2006, Olne had a total population of 3,793. The total area is 15.99 km2 which gives a population density of 237 inhabitants per km2.

Olne was the 24th village to join Les Plus Beaux Villages de Wallonie.

